{"tid":1123864,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"出黎做野之後, 啤酒竟然好飲左....","createTime":"2019-04-24T17:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T00:00:19.000Z","uid":72045,"like":85,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a605585381a420536be2588d8dc21475923b86a5","tid":1123864,"uid":72045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:05:21.000Z","msg":"細過仲會諗D大人真係ON9, 咁苦都飲, 我大過就算飲都飲水果酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇小新果陣好唔明點解廣志會中意飲啤酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大學飲酒開始理解點解大人會飲啤酒, 但都係覺得好苦<br />\n出左黎做野之後, 出去同同事HAPPY HOUR開始覺得啤酒OK, 但係O係屋企自隊都會覺得苦<br />\n到而家做左半年野之後, 係屋企自隊啤酒竟然覺得唔苦, 雖則唔係好飲但係冰涼加少少少苦既感覺真係好痛快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再之後會唔會開始覺得啤酒好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"addec80354cd4bfa6def65ca973034c2fee0ea4b","tid":1123864,"uid":89064,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:06:19.000Z","msg":"飲啤酒簡直係放鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674f85dcc9debd5bbfc59db9e835f8d6c64ef6e9","tid":1123864,"uid":192654,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:12:15.000Z","msg":"喺屋企飲whiskey仲正"},{"pid":"198f7a452d2795090571cdb7c76b1ae3c37bbd6e","tid":1123864,"uid":123020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:14:06.000Z","msg":"其實係想享受醺醉果一刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又未到飲完乜都唔記得晒<br />\n至少係番工前比一刻放鬆既時間我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e110bbc8b47ba5d652d3e4ce71913e34a14a4904","tid":1123864,"uid":55458,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:14:49.000Z","msg":"人生苦<br />\n啤酒更苦"},{"pid":"772815e034bad98e6864c25a14753667d2ee5628","tid":1